---
title: Shawarma Double Beef Meatballs with Roasted Veggie Couscous and Feta Cheese
description: This deconstructed wrap, inspired by the classic Middle Eastern dish, is equally tasty and colourful! Savoury beef meatballs paired with roasted veggies, couscous and sprinkled with salty feta cheese – it's an instant classic.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/boulettes-double-boeuf-style-shawarma-45bd5122.jpg
